<whdroplet name="drDemoSetupHTEM">
<ol>
<li> Requires whSendmail.exe</li>
<li> You will need access to a mail server in order to send email from your machine.
Edit the htMailin.pas file, and customize this line:
<pre>
  MailHost.Hostname:='mail.href.com';   <!--- replace with your mail server -->
</pre></li>
