<whtranslation key="~whDemoShortDescHTEM">
This demo shows how to calculate a quotation based on surfer input, and then send a quotation letter by e-mail. 
</whtranslation>


<whtranslation key="~whDemoLongDescHTEM">
The surfer enters the quantity desired for two items, and a payment method.  Based on this information, 
the application calculates the amount due.  It then generates an email message with fill-ins for the 
calculated values.
</whtranslation>

